snippet.title: Chico and the Magic Orchards DX - Nintendo Switch Trailer
snippet.description:
Chico and the Magic Orchards DX is launching on the Nintendo Switch system on December 29th, 2023! Check it out on Nintendo eShop: 
https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/chico-and-the-magic-orchards-dx-switch/

Solve puzzles by rolling a giant walnut in this retro-handheld-inspired adventure. Explore a variety of levels each with unique mechanics. Help Chico build his winter stash and get home!
